snippet.textDisplay:
Thank you for using chick peas! Also guys, Aqua faba is a great substitute in any egg white cocktail! You can add to almost any citrus based cocktail with a hard shake, which develops a foam top and velvety texture! Top with an aromatic of your choice if you think it smells “beany”.

I’m not vegan and still prefer it to egg white.
